snippet.title: Harmful The Second Tape - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Harmful The Second Tape

"The authorities received a second Tape in early September. They now assumed they had something bigger on their hands. The Contents of the tape were....disturbing."

An atmospheric horror adventure game where you play as both an FBI Investigator and the Killer themselves.

Buy the game here : https://toothandclaw.itch.io/harmful-thesecondtape

Play the first game here : https://toothandclaw.itch.io/harmful
